cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use SmeftFR in your work, please cite the software and the associated publications."
title: "SmeftFR"
abstract: >-
  Mathematica / FeynRules package for deriving Feynman rules for the Standard
  Model Effective Field Theory (SMEFT) directly in the physical mass-eigenstate
  basis, including the complete dimension-6 SMEFT operator set and the complete
  bosonic dimension-8 operator set in version 3.0.
type: software
